<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #000;
        margin: 1in;
        font-size: 11pt;
    }
    h1 {
        font-size: 16pt;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-top: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .ref-item {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        padding-left: 0.5in;
        text-indent: -0.5in;
        text-align: justify;
    }
    .category {
        font-weight: bold;
        text-decoration: underline;
        margin-top: 30px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-size: 12pt;
    }
</style>
<title>References - KaviCakes Management System</title>
</head>
<body>

